{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Ru7f4E9zU6ALpLJf7jpT74","type":"tool_result","content":"Template rendering CLI for LLM code generation workflows\n\nUsage: jig [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>\n\nCommands:\n  validate  Parse a recipe and report whether it is valid\n  vars      Show expected variables for a recipe as JSON\n  render    Render a template with variables\n  run       Execute all file operations in a recipe\n  workflow  Execute a multi-recipe workflow\n  list      List available skills and recipes\n  library   Manage recipe libraries\n  help      Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)\n\nOptions:\n      --vars <VARS>            Inline variables as JSON string\n      --vars-file <VARS_FILE>  Variables from a JSON file\n      --vars-stdin             Read variables from stdin\n      --dry-run                Preview without writing files\n      --json                   Force JSON output to stdout\n      --quiet                  Suppress stderr output\n      --force                  Overwrite existing files\n      --base-dir <BASE_DIR>    Resolve output paths from this directory\n      --verbose                Include rendered content in output\n  -h, --help                   Print help\n  -V, --version                Print version\n---\nExecute all file operations in a recipe\n\nUsage: jig run [OPTIONS] <RECIPE>\n\nArguments:\n  <RECIPE>  Path to the recipe YAML file\n\nOptions:\n      --vars <VARS>            Inline variables as JSON string\n      --vars-file <VARS_FILE>  Variables from a JSON file\n      --vars-stdin             Read variables from stdin\n      --dry-run                Preview without writing files\n      --json                   Force JSON output to stdout\n      --quiet                  Suppress stderr output\n      --force                  Overwrite existing files\n      --base-dir <BASE_DIR>    Resolve output paths from this directory\n      --verbose                Include rendered content in output\n  -h, --help                   Print help","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4080954c-0177-4464-94af-0364f3975113","uuid":"29eecdc2-331f-43e7-857e-60ccf3b4df49"}
